<div type="content"><note place="marginleft"><ab facs="#facs_547_line_1592204547708_2663"><expan>ſ<ex>i</ex>n<ex>e</ex></expan> <expan>ſ<ex>er</ex>uicio</expan> </ab></note>
<ab facs="#facs_547_r1l2">Weygel Strobel als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt / wıe Jr vns vor auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_547_r1l4"><expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von <expan>beschuldıgu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> eẅch kein antwurt von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_547_r1l5">vns worden ſey etc das haben wır <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu ward vns eẅr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_547_r1l6"><expan>nehſt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> als wır <expan>vom<ex>m</ex></expan> Rat awfſteen <expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan> . ſo ıſt ſeıd kein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_547_r1l10">antwurt 
<add><ab facs="#facs_547_line_1592204568588_2690">von <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab></add> ʒu ʒeıten als wır rat gehabt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / an vns <expan>erford<ex>er</ex>t</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> wıſſen </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_547_r1l7">worden </ab></add> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_547_r1l12">Alſo ſüllt Jr wıſſen / daʒ klag 
<add><ab facs="#facs_547_r1l11">von geſten </ab></add> für vns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> ıſt / vvıe Jr vnd ander </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_547_r1l13">des Reıchs ſtraſſen 
<add><ab facs="#facs_547_line_1592204551108_2668">vnd dıe ʒu vnd </ab><ab facs="#facs_547_line_1592204554203_2673">von vns <expan>wand<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> gerawbt vnd beſchedıgt habt . Wölt Jr eẅch nu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_547_r1l16">des gen vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> . wenn Jr denn <expan>hıeʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> ſand Nıclas tag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_547_r1l17">ſchıerıſt ʒu vns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> wölt . ſo ſüllt Jr ʒu vnd von vns fur vns vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_547_r1l18">dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd bey vns für <expan>menikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> iij tag geleyt haben . alſdenn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_547_line_1592204589000_2713"><expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wır eẅr rede hören . <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_547" id="272v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
